:INFO
Set Up the Flood and Drain Cycle
Install a submersible pump in the fish tank that fills the grow bed every 30 minutes and \
drains back by gravity using a bell siphon or a simple standpipe. The roots need both \
wet and dry cycles to stay healthy and oxygenated. Aim for 2 flood and drain

